id: pm-xkgq
title: "Fold aggregate into the query nouns: pm list --group-by/--count-by (or ops stats --by), retire the aggregate top-level"
description: Decide and implement the simplified grammar home for aggregate so grouped counts and rollups remain available through query or ops nouns while the aggregate top-level spelling becomes an alias.
type: Task
status: open
priority: 3
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:cli",cli-simplification
