acceptance_criteria: Grouped-count queries are reachable from a consolidated noun (list or ops stats) with identical output fields; aggregate keeps working as a hidden alias emitting the one-line migration hint per ADR pm-pbyu; contracts/completions/docs/MCP regenerated; spelling-parity spec covers old vs new invocation
parent: pm-n7rr
risk: medium
