dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pm-0z7n,related,"2026-07-06T21:57:53.805Z",null,null
body: "aggregate is the only query-family command left without a consolidation child under pm-n7rr: it does grouped item counts, overlapping both list (filters/projections) and stats (totals, moving under pm ops per pm-6apl). Per ADR pm-pbyu (one noun per domain, projections are flags), fold it as a --group-by/--count-by projection on list, or as ops stats --by. Decide the exact spelling in-item against the grammar table, wire the alias shim via pm-0z7n, and follow the full wiring checklist (commands/index, register-mutation, mcp/server, sdk/cli-contracts, contracts.ts, completions, docs, vitest.config, contracts:update). Depends on the alias shim foundation."
